WEBVTT

00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:03.176
Procedures to make the available

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:04.792
part of the stomach smaller

00:00:04.790 --> 00:00:05.768
are designed to make

00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:07.336
you feel fuller sooner.

00:00:07.720 --> 00:00:10.064
You eat less, so you lose weight.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.544
Gastric banding uses an inflatable

00:00:13.540 --> 00:00:14.992
band placed around the upper

00:00:14.990 --> 00:00:16.040
part of the stomach

00:00:16.208 --> 00:00:17.816
to create a smaller pouch

00:00:17.810 --> 00:00:19.080
from the larger stomach.

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:21.144
The band can be tightened

00:00:21.140 --> 00:00:22.656
or relaxed to control

00:00:22.650 --> 00:00:24.200
the size of the pouch.

